      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"3. MYRNIONG STORM crossed over from out wide last start before finishing second (22.15) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 390m. The form from his last run stacks up well. One of the leading chances. 1. STARSHIP ATLAS finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his handy 22.15 win at Shepparton over 390m. Should be in this for a long way. 6. PAW PASCAL turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Tick Returns (22.35) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Comes through a solid form race last start. Bold showing expected. 8. FAYE VALENTINE did a good job to finish second last time out over 400m at Warragul (23.30) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.\",\"runners\":[3,1,6,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
